00:03:04.605 --> 00:03:08.335
that is used to regulate and push forward a larger disc.

00:03:09.275 --> 00:03:15.335
The concept of a flywheel in business is when there are lots of smaller things happening that

00:03:15.365 --> 00:03:21.645
all support each other, that all help each other, so that the overall object, the overall

00:03:21.676 --> 00:03:27.325
business, moves faster than all of the individual objects would do if they were on their own.

00:03:28.365 --> 00:03:35.945
