00:05:29.482 --> 00:05:34.412
story–without magical characters and magical stories the whole thing would come

00:05:34.472 --> 00:05:40.172
crashing down–but that all these other aspects of the Disney business reinforced

00:05:40.172 --> 00:05:44.642
each other, making the whole this much greater than the sum of its parts.

