Disney builds brands around the main characters in the films, selling the rights to

00:08:13.534 --> 00:08:19.318
merchandise, to things like toys, duvet covers, clothes, video games, you name it.

00:08:19.958 --> 00:08:25.688
Of course, you know this - you may well have bought Disney merchandise - but the way to think

00:08:25.698 --> 00:08:31.608
about this is that there is the story and the characters at the centre of everything, and of course

00:08:31.608 --> 00:08:37.708
these films often make over a billion dollars at the box office, but the way Disney continues

00:08:37.708 --> 00:08:42.578
to make money from it is through everything else that they do with the film and the characters.

00:08:43.408 --> 00:08:45.738
