00:08:45.898 --> 00:08:52.958
Indeed, as we talked about in the last episode, as early as 1930 Walt Disney started

00:08:52.978 --> 00:08:58.268
merchandising Mickey Mouse, he was offered $300 to put Mickey Mouse on some pencils.

