00:11:19.634 --> 00:11:23.574
and important development for Disney, and that’s Disney Plus.

00:11:24.734 --> 00:11:30.034
Disney Plus, in case you hadn’t heard of it, is Disney’s answer to Netflix.

00:11:31.134 --> 00:11:35.304
