Certainly when you compare it to buying the videos or DVDs, which could

00:12:09.944 --> 00:12:16.194
easily be €20, or going to watch it in a cinema, which is easily more than €10

00:12:16.224 --> 00:12:21.274
nowadays, it does seem like an incredible bargain, it seems like very good value.

00:12:22.074 --> 00:12:27.754
